## Development

```bash
npm install
npx serve src
```

Or use any static server:

```bash
python -m http.server 8000 --directory src
```

## Structure

```
src/
├── index.html          # Homepage
├── about.html          # About page
├── contact.html        # Contact page
├── 404.html            # Not found error
├── styles/
│   ├── main.css        # Entry point
│   ├── _reset.css      # CSS reset
│   └── _tokens.css     # Design tokens
├── scripts/
│   └── main.js         # Progressive enhancement
└── images/
    └── favicon.svg     # Site icon
```

## Validation

```bash
npm run lint            # HTML validation
npm run lint:css        # CSS linting
npm run a11y            # Accessibility
npm run lint:spelling   # Spell check
```

## Adding Pages

1. Copy an existing page as template
2. Update `<title>` and meta description
3. Update navigation `aria-current` attributes
4. Add to sitemap.xml

## Theming

Edit `src/styles/_tokens.css` to change the brand color:

```css
:root {
  --hue-primary: 200;  /* Change this value */
}
```

